sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant Lambda as TACT Lambda
    participant Bedrock as Amazon Bedrock (Claude Sonnet 4.5)
    participant DDB as DynamoDB (AuditTrail)
    participant CW as CloudWatch Logs
    
    User->>Frontend: Submit action for evaluation
    Frontend->>APIGW: POST /tact/evaluate
    APIGW->>Lambda: Invoke with payload
    
    Note over Lambda: Build prompt with industry context
    
    Lambda->>Bedrock: InvokeModel - TACT evaluation
    
    Note over Bedrock: Analyze action across 4 dimensions
    
    Bedrock-->>Lambda: JSON Response with scores
    
    Lambda->>DDB: PutItem - Log evaluation
    DDB-->>Lambda: Success
    
    Lambda->>CW: Log execution
    
    Lambda-->>APIGW: Return evaluation result
    APIGW-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>User: Display results
    
    Note over User,CW: Total latency: 800-1200ms
